# .gitignore — Nintendo Switch build output exclusions
# Prevents devkitPro ARM cross-compilation artifacts from being tracked in version control.
# These files are regenerated every build and are platform/architecture-specific binaries.

# Intermediate object files and build artifacts produced by the devkitPro toolchain
/bin
# Nintendo Application Control Property files — metadata (title, author, version) for the Switch OS
/*.nacp
# Nintendo Relocatable Object files — the final homebrew executable loaded by the Switch HBMenu
/*.nro
# Raw ELF binaries produced by the ARM linker before conversion to NRO/NSP format
/*.elf